{
  "texts": [
    "Using a large amount of Internet text data and thousands of books for model training, the latest version-GPT-4, can imitate the natural language patterns of humans nearly perfectly.",
    "This language model is closest to predictability and generates meaningful content.",
    "With the introduction of pre-training on vast amount of text, GPT has acquired a healthy knowledge, which eventually helping us to solve discriminative tasks such as:",
    "• Question answering, • Semantic similarity assessment, • Entailment determination, and • Text classification GPT utilizes a semi-supervised method for NLU, it uses a combination of unsupervised pre-training and supervised fine-tuning.",
    "GPT uses a large amount of unlabeled text and several datasets which are very well annotated pre-hand training examples (target tasks)."
  ]
}